ials to collect, odd characters to meet, and otherworldly mysteries to uncover. Explore them all, to get to the truth.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350490/extras/f3dae6dadd517e3c79e66670a9b89fdd.webp?t=1731959182\" width=600 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350490/extras/540b672ffa1b713c009349f4806229c2.poster.avif?t=1731959182\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350490/extras/540b672ffa1b713c009349f4806229c2.webm?t=1731959182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350490/extras/540b672ffa1b713c009349f4806229c2.mp4?t=1731959182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each character is complicated and unique. Greyzoned and complex. Meet them all, and uncover a deep, dark story through branching dialogue with choices that matters.<br>Get to know characters that might help you on your journey. <i>Might</i>.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350490/extras/fbda066d3d1ae94e7d817a9f4a94c9ba.webp?t=1731959182\" width=600 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350490/extras/f0182a0d33cd2d64a411939258ed9403.poster.avif?t=1731959182\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350490/extras/f0182a0d33cd2d64a411939258ed9403.webm?t=1731959182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350490/extras/f0182a0d33cd2d6